node_3.subject: Honaldu Son
node_3.description: This is Honaldu Son's plan for Tuesday February 14: wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am, inspect crops and harvest fruits and vegetables starting at 8:30 am, give special attention to animals starting at 1:00 pm, head to village to greet neighbors at 3:00 pm, come back home and have dinner with family at 6:00 pm.

node_2.subject: Honaldu Son
node_2.description: This is Honaldu Son's plan for Tuesday February 14: wake up and complete the morning routine at 4:00 am, check the fields, harvest ripe fruits and vegetables, complete equipment maintenance and repair from 4:00 am to 12:00 pm, have a lunch at 12:00 pm, take care of livestock from 1 to 4 pm, go around the village and greet the villagers at 4:00 pm, have a dinner at home at 6:00 pm, take a shower and relax at home from 7:00 pm to 11:00 pm.
